<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="a7Apr1935"><font color="red">7 April 1935</font> <i>Letters I</i> (to Harriet Weaver): Perhaps I shall survive, and perhaps the raving madness I write will survive. And perhaps it is very funny. One thing is sure, however. <i>Je suis bien triste</i>. </div>
